: 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.035428648613379e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  A collaboration between Raducanu and Murray could help Emma reach new heights in an already impressive career, but it now appears unlikely to come to fruition.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9676189707686846e-33, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.998784055341952, \"rank\": 0.0010259648041821845, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only did the 21-year-old pull out of competing with Murray in the mixed doubles ofWimbledonthis summer due to injury concerns, but Murray has already been tutoring 17-year-old Charlie Robertson.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9676189707686846e-33, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9676189707686846e-33, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4767786061906564e-15, \"text\": \"Charlie Robertson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, Andy's mother Judy shared a snap of the two side by side on the courts - writing: \\\"Charlie Robertson: the teenage Scot following in Andy's footsteps is heading to New York next month to compete in the boys singles at the US Open.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4767786061906564e-15, \"text\": \"Charlie Robertson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Robertson\"}, {\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999998435223583, \"rank\": 1.5142285142190566e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's ranked 25 in the world juniors and has just spent a week as Andy's training partner as he prepares for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's 20 years since Andy won the US Open junior event in 2004 and it's great to see him investing in the next generation.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.935861658826044, \"rank\": 0.027464247762228403, \"text\": \"US Open\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/US_Open_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No better and quicker way to learn than working alongside someone who has been there and done it.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go Charlie.\\\"\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after Sue Barker highlighted how Murray previously showed interest in stepping into the world of coaching during her Monday Mile with Aimee Fuller.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Barker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sue Barker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Barker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Barker\"}, {\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9676189707686846e-33, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fuller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aimee Fuller\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fuller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fuller\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chatting on The Walking podcast, she said: \\\"Do you know, it was interesting Aims when he said 'I'd like to be in the coaching box', and I thought 'I wonder if he's got a young player that he's got his eye on that he wants to mentor and bring forward' because that would be fantastic.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Can you imagine havingAndy Murrayas your coach, I mean, he was the ultimate tactician, he knows how to play the big points probably better than anybody.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And to have him in your corner, teaching you tennis and teaching you the mindset...oh my word.\\\"\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raducanu left Murray hanging when she pulled out of the mixed doubles tournament atWimbledonthis summer, after he had been eliminated from the men's doubles with brother Jamie.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2750, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9676189707686846e-33, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy had been forced to bail on the singles tournament due to not being fully fit following his back operation.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Ra